data.description: Why rent when you can own! Welcome home to this beautiful brick house with over 1800 square feet of living space. This home features a newer roof, windows, renovated bathroom and vinyl flooring and carpeting throughout. Separate living room and family room gives everyone the space they need to relax.  2nd floor offers a large 3rd bedroom or extra living space. On top of that, the fenced back yard with patio for grilling and detached garage offer plenty of room for entertaining. Come take a look today!
